headline: Interactive Brokers Group to Host Second Quarter Earnings Conference Call
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., June 26, 2025--Interactive Brokers Group, Inc. (Nasdaq: IBKR) plans to announce its second quarter financial results on Thursday, July 17, 2025, in a release that will be issued at approximately 4:00 pm (ET). The press release will also be available on the company's website, www.interactivebrokers.com/ir.
